5. Multiplication (MUL) Operation
Modify (Machine Ins)
-> Instructions
-> New
-> MUL
-> Opcode = 0x8
Implementation (Fetch Operand)
-> DR ← MAIN[AR]
-> dis - read
-> data - DR
-> add - AR
Drag DR ← MAIN[AR] for multiplying
go to Arithmetic Ins.
Name: MUL
ACC ← AC * DR
Source 1 = AC
Source 2 = DR
Type = multiplication
Dest = AC
Carry bit (Set if result overflows register size)
Drag it AC ← AC * DR (Arithmetic)
Now Machine is Ready.
Execute it
